		text = '#C0x5B545B# has been placed #C0xF76B45##L10#2#C0xFF5B545B##L0# runestones, after consumption #C0xF76B45##L10# can only be replaced with 1 new runestone #C0xFF5B545B##L0# (like Runestone If it has been strengthened, then the reinforced materials will be returned free of charge.) Are replacements confirmed?',
